	<internal-name>Sec 1</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-bottom</sectionClass_s>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;What are the different types of investments?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;There are many different ways to invest your money in Mzansi. The technical financial term for these different options is &amp;lsquo;asset classes&amp;rsquo;. Asset classes vary wildly and range from classes with terms you&amp;rsquo;ll be familiar with - like shares, and property ownership, to ones you might not have heard of before, like commodities, futures and derivatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Luckily for you, if you are interested in investing, you don&amp;rsquo;t need to know everything there is to know about which asset classes are which, and which ones are right for you. That&amp;rsquo;s our job. So, remember, your Velocity Club relationship consultant is only a phone call away and has all the latest and best investment information to help you make the right decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s the right investment for you?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re glad you asked!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s no one answer that is going to work for every single person. But there are things that you need to consider when making a decision to invest. Those are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your financial health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your budget&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your tolerance for risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;1. Your financial health&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;ve read this far you&amp;rsquo;re no doubt eager to start building your own investment portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;But first, you need to understand your financial health and make sure that you are getting started on the right foot. If you haven&amp;rsquo;t done so yet, feel free to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent; color: var(--color-black);" data-tf-slider="Sgz7HGMv" data-tf-width="550" data-tf-hidden="utm_source=CTA,utm_medium=website,utm_campaign=velocityclub_site,utm_term=,utm_content=" data-tf-loaded="true"&gt;book a session&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;with us to see where your finances stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Once that&amp;rsquo;s done, the next step is to start actively paying off your expensive debt, especially credit card debt. This has a high interest rate and until it&amp;rsquo;s paid off, you'll struggle to get ahead with your investing. That&amp;rsquo;s because if your investment gains don&amp;rsquo;t outperform your losses to interest payments, you&amp;rsquo;ll basically be &amp;lsquo;investing yourself poorer&amp;rsquo; as we like to say.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;We also recommend that you have a proper emergency fund in place, or at least that you&amp;rsquo;re building one up. This is money you&amp;rsquo;ve saved, to carry you through life&amp;rsquo;s unexpected dramas. This could be anything from your car needing new tyres, to funding your expenses if you get retrenched. This way you don&amp;rsquo;t need to use expensive debt to get back on your feet.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
