	<internal-name>Conclusion</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s/>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Investing is a broad topic that&amp;rsquo;s difficult to cover in a single blog post but we hope that you&amp;rsquo;ve got a better understanding of investing now than before you started reading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;In this post, we explained the difference between investing and saving. We touched on the different kinds of investments available to you. And finally, we looked at the factors that one must take into consideration when we decide to start investing. The four factors were financial health, time, your budget, and your risk tolerance. These will differ from person to person and so every person&amp;rsquo;s investment decision will be different.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re a complete beginner and would like to start investing, contact your Velocity Club relationship consultant and they&amp;rsquo;ll help you make investment decisions that are right for you and your financial goals. If you don&amp;rsquo;t yet have a subscription to Velocity Club,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="background-color: transparent;" href="/money-plan.html"&gt;click here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to find out more and to sign up!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;button class="btn btn--primary get_started_post_three_navbar_button" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: var(--btn-font-size); line-height: 1; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; appearance: button; display: inline-flex; position: relative; white-space: nowrap; justify-content: center; padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm); border-radius: var(--btn-radius); border-color: transparent; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; cursor: pointer; background-color: #e01f26; min-width: 196px; color: #ffffff !important;" role="button" data-tf-slider="Sgz7HGMv" data-tf-width="550" data-tf-hidden="utm_source=CTA,utm_medium=website,utm_campaign=velocityclub_site,utm_term=,utm_content=" data-tf-loaded="true"&gt;Book a session&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
